/div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd6 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">他死后安葬于英国皇家教堂——西敏寺<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="fs4 ls56">（Westminster <span class="_ _f"></span>Abbey）</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yb7 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls27 ws0">的“诗人之角”<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls26">，在那里，还有莎士比亚、达尔文、丘吉尔</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yb8 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">等名人的墓碑。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 yd7 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">还有爱因斯坦，<span class="_ _5"></span>他生前在遗嘱中要求，<span class="_ _4"></span>把骨灰撒在不为</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">人知的地方，<span class="_ _4"></span>不建坟墓。<span class="_ _6"></span>但一个叫哈维的美国医生，<span class="_ _4"></span>却偷偷</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
